From efa6f03405bb8da550bf0c206d714230b2ab354c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: laokz <zhangkai@iscas.ac.cn>
Date: Wed, 6 Mar 2024 20:47:18 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] riscv64: upatch-diff adapt common arch data

1. RISC-V has mapping symbol like ARM.

2. not support line_macro_change_only. It's less
value compared to the big complexity.
---
